{"tid":1237582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲未有共識？下一步點做？唔通你覺得已經成功左？","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:24:33.000Z","uid":233600,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"314ac24e260c0628ffddded9074e9479e7ada4bc","tid":1237582,"uid":233600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"一百萬又好，二百萬零一人都好，我地爭取左啲乜野？<br />\n暫緩？<br />\n道歉？<br />\n催淚彈？<br />\n胡椒噴霧？<br />\n定係布袋彈？<br />\n到頭黎我地爭取左啲乜？<br />\n點解我要日曬雨淋出黎行出黎企？<br />\n又點解我要食催淚彈？<br />\n點解要學生食子彈？<br />\n...點解要有人死？<br />\n休息夠, 就企返起身。<br />\n記住呢個係一個唔會完結嘅夢。<br />\n係時候要討論下一步啦, 香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />620<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />621"},{"pid":"05775195049ac79faedad8bed8f0a7ee67ec35cb","tid":1237582,"uid":233600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"點解要當一切嘅野都係發夢？<br />\n我唔想再發夢啦。"},{"pid":"a3e30888bca1349019ca0f007c603ce4c56256aa","tid":1237582,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzieVOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzieVOh.png&h=81de3cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMzE6UZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMzE6UZ.png&h=79446625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QLg88m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QLg88m.png&h=101a8560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0a1AOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0a1AOn.png&h=873d2d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GdFRmJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GdFRmJ.png&h=1f5cc154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9j080e4.png\" data